          <a href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/the-corona-crisis-and-getting-to-globalisation-we-need/">
            <h1 class="mt-1 mt-md-2">
              The Corona-crisis and getting to the globalisation we need            </h1>
            <div class="d-none d-md-block">
              <p>The Coronavirus outbreak is one of the most urgent and existential global challenges our world has seen in generations.  Like nothing before it, it has shown how economically, technologically, politically and environmentally interconnected our world is. We do need to reinvent how globalisation works, and place active citizenship at its core.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <span
            class="my-2 d-inline-block source__name"><a href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/author/omri-preiss/" title="Posts by Omri Preiss" class="author url fn" rel="author">Omri Preiss</a>, <a href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/author/nikola-ilic/" title="Posts by Nikola Ilic" class="author url fn" rel="author">Nikola Ilic</a>                        </span>
                  </article>
                  </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12 align-mobile">
      <div class="autopromo mt-4 mt-sm-0">
  <div class="description text-center mt-3 mb-3">
    Voxeurop is the first European Press Cooperative – owned by journalists, translators, and readers in 16 countries.  </div>
